OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779466274
OL,3,CWelsh Water issues notice to boil
OL,4,Cwater before drinking after treatment
OL,5,Cissue
OL,7,FDwr Cymru has issued a warning to
OL,8,Fthose living in certain areas of south
OL,9,FWales to boil their water before using
OL,10,Fit to drink or cook.
OL,12,FIt follows an issues identified with
OL,13,Fits Maerdy Water Treatment Works. The
OL,14,Fboil water notice covers an area of
OL,15,Fthe Rhondda and wider Rhondda Cynon
OL,16,FTaf area.
