PN,46202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779466274
OL,3,CWelsh Water issues notice to boil
OL,4,Cwater before drinking after treatment
OL,5,Cissue
OL,7,FIn a notice published by Welsh Water,
OL,8,Fit said an issue was identified "with
OL,9,Fthe chemical process" used to treat
OL,10,Fdrinking water during routine checks
OL,11,Fat the works on Friday morning.
OL,13,FThe organisation has temporarily
OL,14,Fstopped water from the site entering
OL,15,Fthe network, as a precaution, while
OL,16,Fthe issue is being resolved.
OL,18,FCustomers will continue to receive
OL,19,Fwater supplies and Welsh Water says it
OL,20,Fdoes not expect any loss of service.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
