PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779466274
OL,3,CWelsh Water issues notice to boil
OL,4,Cwater before drinking after treatment
OL,5,Cissue
OL,7,FHowever, customers in certain areas
OL,8,Fhave been advised to boil their water
OL,9,Fwith immediate effect before using it
OL,10,Ffor drinking, brushing teeth, making
OL,11,Fice and cooking purposes.
OL,13,FThe affected areas are:
OL,15,FWelsh Water said customers who are
OL,16,Fimpacted are being sent a text. You
OL,17,Fcan check if you area is affected
OL,18,Fusing the postcode checker here.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
