PN,46204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779466274
OL,3,CWelsh Water issues notice to boil
OL,4,Cwater before drinking after treatment
OL,5,Cissue
OL,7,FIn response to the statement posted on
OL,8,FFacebook, several customers said they
OL,9,Fhad already drank water from their
OL,10,Ftaps or had given it to their children
OL,11,Fbefore school.
OL,13,F"Oh great just seen this and I've had
OL,14,Fa litre to drink today - no text and
OL,15,Fin the affected area," one customer
OL,16,Fwrote.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
