PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1779466274
OL,3,CWelsh Water issues notice to boil
OL,4,Cwater before drinking after treatment
OL,5,Cissue
OL,7,F"One of my kids has already had three
OL,8,Fcups this morning. Apparently there
OL,9,Fwas meant to have been texts gone out,
OL,10,Fhave received none, I only knew
OL,11,Fbecause my eldest works in Tylorstown
OL,12,Fand messaged me," another wrote.
OL,14,FBottled water stations are being set
OL,15,Fup and will provide bottled water
OL,16,Fdirectly to the most vulnerable
OL,17,Fcustomers registered on the
OL,18,Forganisation's Priority Services
OL,19,FRegister.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
